15
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:27,920
to infringe upon the equality and freedom of the people.

16
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:29,600
I thought about it for some time,

17
00:00:29,920 --> 00:00:30,960
as long as you do these two things,

18
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,877
[Hu Shi, styled Shizhi, Professor at Peking University]
[Li Dazhao, styled Shouchang, Director of Peking University Library]

19
00:00:31,200 --> 00:00:33,120
then justice must triumph over power.

20
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:34,320
So I plan

21
00:00:34,400 --> 00:00:35,520
to write an article in the next issue

22
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:36,480
of "Weekly Review"

23
00:00:37,040 --> 00:00:38,080
to talk about

24
00:00:38,160 --> 00:00:39,600
